sentiment_score_definition: x <= -0.35: Bearish; -0.35 < x <= -0.15: Somewhat-Bearish; -0.15 < x < 0.15: Neutral; 0.15 <= x < 0.35: Somewhat_Bullish; x >= 0.35: Bullish

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Acquisition adjourns shareholder meeting to December 22 By Investing.com
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corp has announced the adjournment of its extraordinary general meeting of shareholders to December 22, 2025, at 10:00 AM Eastern Time. Shareholders can change or revoke their prior votes until 11:59 PM ET on December 21, 2025, and those who have submitted redemption requests can withdraw them. This follows recent approvals for extending the business combination deadline and the appointment of a new director.

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Acquisition appoints Dr. Xunyong Zhou as director By Investing.com
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corp has announced the appointment of Dr. Xunyong Zhou to its board of directors. Dr. Zhou brings extensive experience in biotechnology and health innovation, holding several patents and leadership roles in related companies. The SPAC, currently trading at $16.45 per unit, appears overvalued based on InvestingPro data, though it has recently made strategic announcements regarding a business combination extension and a non-redemption agreement.

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Acquisition appoints Dr. Xunyong Zhou as director By Investing.com
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corp has appointed Dr. Xunyong Zhou as a director to its board. Dr. Zhou brings extensive experience in biotechnology and health innovation, with a focus on enzyme-based solutions and cell therapy technologies. The company is currently trading at $16.45 per unit and has a market capitalization of approximately $96 million.

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Acquisition enters non-redemption agreement with shareholder
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corporation has inked a non-redemption agreement with an unaffiliated third-party shareholder, involving 600,000 ordinary shares. This agreement, made with the company's sponsor, DT Cloud Star Management Limited, prevents the shareholder from redeeming these shares at an upcoming meeting focused on extending the business combination deadline. In exchange, the shareholder will receive 200,000 ordinary shares upon the closing of the initial business combination.

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Schedules Shareholder Meeting Adjournment
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corporation (DTSQ) announced the adjournment of its annual general meeting of shareholders from October 15, 2025, to October 20, 2025. This allows shareholders to modify or revoke their votes and redemption requests until October 19, 2025, for proposals previously outlined in its proxy statement. DTSQ (stock symbol DTSQ) has an average trading volume of 44,844 and a technical sentiment signal of "Strong Buy."

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Schedules Shareholder Meeting Adjournment - TipRanks
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corporation (DTSQ) has announced the adjournment of its annual general meeting of shareholders to October 20, 2025. feed.title: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corp Reconvenes Annual Meeting - TradingView
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corp announced on October 15, 2025, that its annual general meeting would be reconvened. The meeting has been adjourned to October 20, 2025, at 10:00 AM ET. Shareholders have until October 19, 2025, to change their votes, and redemption requests can be withdrawn by contacting VStock Transfer.

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Acquisition (NASDAQ:DTSQ) Receives Sell (D) Rating from Weiss Ratings - MarketBeat
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition (NASDAQ:DTSQ) recently received a "sell (D)" rating from Weiss Ratings amidst a 0.2% increase in its stock price to $10.50, despite low trading volumes. Institutional investors, however, have significantly increased their stakes in the company, showcasing a divergence in sentiment compared to the Weiss Ratings assessment. The company, incorporated in 2022 and based in Brooklyn, New York, focuses on business combinations.

feed.title: DT Cloud Star Meeting Adjourned to October 15
feed.summary: DT Cloud Star Acquisition Corporation (DTSQ) announced that its annual general meeting of shareholders, held on October 7, 2025, was adjourned without conducting any business besides the adjournment itself. The meeting is scheduled to reconvene on October 15, 2025.
